{"tid":2117881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【直播】7.21 香港民研公佈最新社會指標 自由及法治民調報告","createTime":"2020-07-21T06:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T07:53:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ff1659184840462c4b516d7c4da54ebffaa0e934","tid":2117881,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:47:42.000Z","msg":"【直播】7.21 香港民研公佈最新社會指標 自由及法治民調報告<br />\n20200721<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZMR6j_iW1Bw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZMR6j_iW1Bw&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=d06b4283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZMR6j_iW1Bw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《看中國》香港頻道<br />\n155K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n我們是看中國駐香港的記者，每天奔走在充斥著警笛聲、槍聲、哭喊聲和催淚瓦斯煙霧的街頭，這樣的生活已經持續了一年多。說心裏話，我們不可能沒有恐懼。但是今天我們已越來越從容，在這塊曾經無比繁華的土地上，我們會繼續奔走，用鏡頭把真實的香港展現給你。<br />\n看中國是一個由義工組成的大家庭。我們不僅報導真實的香港，每年都會有數以億計的中國人，通過我們的網站看到真實的中國與真實的世界。這是我們無懼風雨前行的動力。但是我們獨立報導的媒體渠道不斷的被Facebook YouTube審查、降級、甚至關閉。<br />\n加入榮譽會員和我們一起守護香港、守護14億中國人，獲得真實資訊的權利。<br />\n❤ <a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/kzgd/subs...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fkzgd%2Fsubs...&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=6387c5bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/kzgd/subs...</a> ❤<br />\n本視頻僅代表嘉賓或受訪者本人觀點。"},{"pid":"5ef44b63ed6d7ee5bfb803e80f7ca55954593a23","tid":2117881,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:48:53.000Z","msg":"自由指標全線下跌"},{"pid":"ef7afb6b777a8ac8f70de3fc182d792f6e3ae1c4","tid":2117881,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ef44b63ed6d7ee5bfb803e80f7ca55954593a23","tid":2117881,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:48:53.000Z","msg":"自由指標全線下跌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"97年6月 有紀錄以嚟新低"},{"pid":"624e8b236349af0ac1b9ddd02ccb56f125b114b4","tid":2117881,"u